auto italia holdings ltd (720) Details


			Auto Italia Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the trade of cars and related accessories; and provision of car repairing services in Hong Kong and Mainland China. It primarily offers Ferrari and Maserati cars. The company operates in Cars, Financial Investments and Services, and Other segments. It provides pre-delivery inspection consultancy services and warranting services for Ferrari and Maserati cars in Shanghai, China; and financing and corporate finance services, as well as invests in securities and properties. The company was formerly known as Wo Kee Hong (Holdings) Limited and changed its name to Auto Italia Holdings Limited in September 2012. Auto Italia Holdings Limited was incorporated in 1989 and is based in Sha Tin, Hong Kong.
  			

