Auto Italia Holdings Limited, Annual General Meeting, May 25, 2017
Apr 12 17
Auto Italia Holdings Limited, Annual General Meeting, May 25, 2017, at 15:30 China Standard Time. Location: Seminar Room, Level 3 Three Pacific Place, 1 Queen's Road East Hong Kong Agenda: To receive and consider the audited consolidated financial statements and the reports of the directors and the auditor of the company for the year ended 31 December 2016; to re-elect directors; to authorize the board of directors to fix the remuneration of the directors; to authorize the board to re-appoint Messrs. Deloitte Touche Tohmatsu as the independent auditor of the company and to fix its remuneration; to grant a general mandate to the directors of the company to allot, issue and deal with new shares of the company; to grant a general mandate to the directors of the company to repurchase shares of the company; and to extend the general mandate to allot, issue and deal with new shares of the company.


Auto Italia Holdings Limited Reports Audited Consolidated Earnings Results for the Full Year Ended December 31, 2016
Mar 28 17
Auto Italia Holdings Limited reported audited consolidated earnings results for the full year ended December 31, 2016. For the year, revenue was HKD 742,484,000 against HKD 973,140,000 a year ago. Loss before taxation was HKD 6,767,000 against profit before taxation of HKD 37,359,000 a year ago. Loss for the year was HKD 12,375,000 against profit for the year of HKD 27,756,000 a year ago. Diluted earnings per share were 0.24 cent against 0.53 cent a year ago.


Auto Italia Holdings Limited to Report Fiscal Year 2016 Final Results on Mar 28, 2017
Mar 16 17
Auto Italia Holdings Limited announced that they will report fiscal year 2016 final results on Mar 28, 2017








