Business Summary


Operates as an investment holding company, which engages in the import, marketing and distribution of luxury and ultra-luxury carsAuto Italia Holdings Ltd. engages in the activities of the import, marketing and distribution of luxury and ultra-luxury cars.The company operates through the following segments: Cars; Financial Investments and Services, and Property Investment.The Cars segment engages in trading of cars and related accessories and provision of car repairing services.The Financial Investments and Services segment includes provision for financing and corporate finance services.The Property Investment segment engages in development of Properties . The company  was founded by Lee Wing Sum in 1954 and is headquartered in Hong Kong.Number of employees : 222 persons.
 





